'''''iD''''' is a [[video game]] developed by [[Mel Croucher]] and Colin Jones for the [[ZX Spectrum]] and published by [[CRL Group PLC|CRL]] in 1986. The game is text-based and takes the form of a conversation with an entity that has inhabited the computer. The player's task is to gain the entity's trust and find out what other inanimate objects this entity has inhabited in the past.

